Package events

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    JoinedNewGuild
    Description:
    The JoinedNewGuild class defines the event for when the bot joins a new guild.
    LeftGuild
    Description:
    The LeftGuild class defines the event for when the bot leaves a guild.
    MemberJoinedGuild
    Description:
    The MemberJoinedGuild class defines the event for when someone joins a guild that the bot resides in.
    MemberLeftGuild
    Description:
    The MemberLeftGuild class defines the event for when someone is removed from a guild, whether by choice or by force.
